data.description: Welcome to this Cobbs Creek home that was renovated in 2017 and has been kept in good condition since. This home features an open concept on the main level, stainless steel appliances, central air conditioning, a full basement, and a fenced in backyard. This home is offered in as-is, where is condition, and the seller will not complete any buyer requested or lender required repairs post completion of the property appraisal. Its currently tenant occupied, and it's required to give 24-hour notice for all showing requests. Please don't approach the property, tenants or occupants without receiving prior authorization.
